Comment: 0,0:24:54.97,0:24:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,----------------in--------------
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.27,0:04:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)\an8}恳请您
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.37,0:04:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)\an8}打开这扇门
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.93,0:05:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)\an8}我无法抛下痛苦的你不管
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.47,0:05:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)\an8}听我说 这只是一时的梦境
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.16,0:05:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)\an8}我现在的歌声 也仅存于梦中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.98,0:07:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)\an8}世间最珍贵之物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.77,0:07:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)\an8}莫过于美妙的歌声
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.26,0:07:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)\an8}美丽代表一切的这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.64,0:08:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)\an8}赞颂吧 敬畏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.87,0:08:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)\an8}还…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.26,0:08:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)\an8}美丽代表一切的这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.63,0:08:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)\an8}赞颂吧 敬畏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.87,0:08:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)\an8}还有 仰望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.84,0:15:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)\an8}我已经疲惫不堪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.24,0:15:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)\an8}怨恨着世界
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.25,0:16:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)\an8}可衰老的躯体已到极限
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.29,0:16:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)\an8}只求有人能剥去我身上的石壳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.44,0:18:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)\an8}积攒于石壳中的燥热
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.29,0:18:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)\an8}仿佛在灼烧着我的心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.19,0:18:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)\an8}为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.92,0:18:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)\an8}为什么我会受到这样的惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.96,0:18:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)\an8}啊～ 既然终将化为灰烬
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.49,0:18:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)\an8}不如在烈火中燃烧殆尽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.32,0:19:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)\an8}将这不能给我爱的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.31,0:19:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)\an8}我来为你歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.21,0:19:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)\an8}给你的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.99,0:19:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)\an8}对你的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.91,0:19:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)\an8}你的软弱 还有痛苦的身姿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.54,0:19:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)\an8}我都会一直爱下去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.90,0:22:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)\an8}宝石般闪耀的外表
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.33,0:22:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)\an8}美丽而又脆弱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.60,0:22:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)\an8}躲在高处的心灵高贵却又软弱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.58,0:22:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)\an8}掩盖光芒 紧闭门扉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.57,0:22:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)\an8}真实的情感 已经打开心扉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.60,0:22:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)\an8}我相信那耀眼光辉和美丽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.85,0:22:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)\an8}因为钥匙就在心中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.80,0:23:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)\an8}帷幕已经拉开 和照耀在阳光下的你一起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.00,0:23:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)\an8}获得飞出鸟笼的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.30,0:23:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(300,300)\an8}来吧 和一时的美梦说再见
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.02,0:23:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,
